---
title: Shredded Chicken and Ginger Soup in a Mushroom Broth
description: This soup is full of juicy chicken, hearty mushrooms and springy zucchini ribbons. Topped with sesame and chilli-garlic sauce, dinner tonight is impressive and simple to create!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/shredded-chicken-and-ginger-soup-e08cf549-d5c29f49.jpg
